      "rationale": "Validation activities include Couette-flow hemolysis calibration and pump-level pressure-head validation at CPB-relevant operating conditions. The FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry is used as the validation platform, which is representative of the COU device class. Validation is judged sufficient for MRL 2."
    },
